ActorTalk: Why are you back so early? You delivered all the letters?
Um, there was a bit of a... situation...
I ran into an Engineering Force checkpoint. Took off running... and lost the paper copy of the list.
I-I panicked. I don't remember exactly... Probably near the stairs by Kuroro Coffee...
...We gave you a physical copy in the first place to avoid leaving a digital trail. One that could leak.
If someone picks up that list and it gets out, the guild will come after both of us!
I'll bring a few people to help you look. But if we don't find it, you're in serious trouble!
